    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン！
どこにいんだよ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Norn! Where are you!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;？
どこ行くんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt;? Where are you going?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よくぞ、
あなたは自分たちの罪を
受け入れました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Welcome. I see you have
accepted your sins.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt;...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まさか……
&lt;Couleur&gt;がノルンさん……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No way...&lt;Couleur&gt; was Miss Norn...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ずっとあなた方を
そばで見させてもらいました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It was the best way to
keep a close eye on you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン！　ぼくに
この子たちを育てさせたのは、
全部今日のため？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Norn! You made me raise the twins and
set everything up, just for this moment?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>315984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりに、
自分たちの手で、罪を
償わせるためだったんですか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You've done everything so that these
two would atone for their sins?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうです。
ここまでの旅もすべて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Correct. Everything about this journey...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その罪に向き合う覚悟を
育てるために私が与えた試練</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I bestowed them this trial so
that they might temper their
resolution to face their sins.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうして……そんな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-Why...would you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどいと思いますか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>..."Do such a cruel thing", you ask?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどいよ……
ひどすぎます……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's too cruel! It's way too much!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ならば、あなたが
彼らの因果の糸をつなぐ
結び目になりますか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you suggest we resolve
this twisted karma in a
different manner?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊であるあなた。
その魂を使えば
ふたりは助かる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Since you are a Spirit, it is possible
to use your essence to save them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>代わりにあなたが消える</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, you will vanish from
existence in their place.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ふたりが消えたくない
って言うなラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If it means they won't have to disappear...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼく、喜んで、
この身を捧げます！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then I will gladly offer
myself as a sacrifice!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>316988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やめて！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>STOP!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……これが
ふたりの決断なら……
ぼくはその覚悟を受け止める</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...if this is what my twins
wanted...then i'll accept it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>つらいよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is hard...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きみたちを
失いたくはないよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't want to lose you, kids...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Still...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもたちを救うのは
親ではないのですか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is the job of a parent
to save their children.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもたちのした決意を
尊重するのも親です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, but it is also the job of a
parent to respect their decisions.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それが間違った決意でも？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And what if they chose wrong?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もうふたりが間違ってるか
どうか、判断するのは
ぼくじゃないんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whether their resolve is right or
not, it's not my place to judge.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりはもう
それができる……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is their responsibility...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたちは、
覚悟を決めました。
だから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've already decided what
we have to do... So please...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう、エトは関係ない！
エトを離せ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just leave Eto out of this! Let her go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトス、
本当にそれで
よいのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ethos. Is this really acceptable?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>317984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりの存在は、
彼らの未来はここで
失われるのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These two's existence along
with their future will end.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;と&lt;Mel&gt;の、
未来……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt;'s future...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『なりきり士』として、
ふたりが見ていた未来です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They have a future of helping
people as Roleplayers.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もうやめて！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>J-Just STOP!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イジめるなぁあっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>STOP TORMENTING ETO!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;、
エトを取り戻すぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;! Let's take Eto back!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ご覧なさい。彼らは
あなたを取り返すために、
私に立ち向かおうとしています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Look at this. They would
face me to rescue you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>愚かだと思いませんか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't that simply foolish?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Dio&gt;と&lt;Mel&gt;を
バカにするな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Don't insult &lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>318852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぉおおおっ！
やぁああっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uuaaagh!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>45</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>319008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_330_010_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦うと言うのならば、
受けて立ちましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If it is a fight you want,
I will gladly give you one.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
